- Docker (optional)

### Installation

1. Install dependencies:
```bash
go mod download
```

2. Set up environment variables:
```bash
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your configuration
```

3. Run the application:
```bash
go run main.go
```

The API will be available at `http://localhost:8080`

